---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Buzz Co Curbing"
  description="Privacy policy for Buzz Co Curbing. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information."
  noindex={true}
>
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-40 md:pb-32 bg-warm-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8">
      <p class="font-data text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-warm-muted mb-4">LEGAL</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-section-heading font-bold text-dark mb-12">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none font-body text-dark/80 space-y-8">
        <p class="text-sm text-dark/50">Effective date: April 9, 2026</p>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>When you request an estimate, contact us, or use our website, we may collect the following information:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li>Full name</li>
            <li>Phone number</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Property address or general location</li>
            <li>Project details you provide (curb style, linear footage, notes, etc.)</li>
            <li>Device and browser information collected automatically through cookies and analytics tools</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li>Respond to your estimate requests and inquiries</li>
            <li>Schedule and perform curbing services</li>
            <li>Send transactional SMS messages such as appointment reminders, estimate follow-ups, and service notifications (if you opt in)</li>
            <li>Send promotional SMS messages such as seasonal offers and special promotions (if you opt in)</li>
            <li>Communicate with you about your project via phone or email</li>
            <li>Improve our website, services, and customer experience</li>
            <li>Analyze website traffic and usage patterns</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-4">SMS Opt-In and Messaging</h2>
          <p>When you submit our estimate form, you may opt in to receive SMS messages from Buzz Co Curbing. There are two separate opt-in categories:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Transactional messages:</strong> Appointment reminders, estimate follow-ups, and service notifications related to your project.</li>
            <li><strong>Marketing messages:</strong> Promotional offers, seasonal discounts, and special deals.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4">Both opt-ins are optional and are not required to submit the form or receive services. Message frequency may vary. Message and data rates may apply.</p>
          <p class="mt-3">You can opt out at any time by replying <strong>STOP</strong> to any message. For help, reply <strong>HELP</strong> or contact us at <a href="mailto:info@buzzcocurb.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">info@buzzcocurb.com</a>.</p>
          <p class="mt-4 font-semibold text-dark">We will never share, sell, or distribute your SMS opt-in consent or phone number to any third parties or affiliates for marketing or promotional purposes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-4">Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
          <p>Our website uses cookies and similar tracking technologies to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li>Remember your preferences and improve your browsing experience</li>
            <li>Analyze website traffic and usage through tools such as Google Analytics</li>
            <li>Support advertising and marketing campaigns (e.g., Google Ads, Meta Pixel)</li>
            <li>Track UTM parameters and referral sources to measure campaign performance</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">You can manage or disable cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect certain website functionality.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-4">Data Security</h2>
          <p>We implement reasonable administrative, technical, and physical safeguards to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, loss, alteration, or misuse. These measures include encrypted data transmission (SSL/TLS), secure hosting infrastructure, and restricted access to personal data.</p>
          <p class="mt-3">However, no method of electronic transmission or storage is 100% secure. While we strive to protect your information, we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-4">Third-Party Service Providers</h2>
          <p>We may share your information with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our business, including:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li>CRM and lead management platforms</li>
            <li>SMS messaging providers (for delivering opted-in messages only)</li>
            <li>Website analytics providers</li>
            <li>Advertising platforms</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">These providers are contractually required to protect your information and may only use it for the specific services we engage them to perform. We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Access</strong> the personal information we hold about you</li>
            <li><strong>Correct</strong> inaccurate or incomplete information</li>
            <li><strong>Delete</strong> your personal information from our systems</li>
            <li><strong>Opt out</strong> of SMS messages at any time by replying STOP</li>
            <li><strong>Opt out</strong> of marketing emails by clicking the unsubscribe link in any email</li>
            <li><strong>Withdraw consent</strong> for data processing where consent was the basis</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@buzzcocurb.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">info@buzzcocurb.com</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we do, we will revise the effective date at the top of this page. Continued use of our website or services after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-card border border-dark/[0.06] bg-warm-gray p-8">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your data, contact us at:</p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            <strong>Buzz Co Curbing</strong><br />
            Email: <a href="mailto:info@buzzcocurb.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">info@buzzcocurb.com</a><br />
            Website: <a href="https://www.buzzcocurb.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">www.buzzcocurb.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
